[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    13[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;192;197;206mThe Technology section's "Why Death Status Is Not a Field on a Record" subsection is the chapter's clearest articulation of why the simple [38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;163;190;140mdeceased_flag[38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;192;197;206m boolean and [38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;163;190;140mdate_of_death[38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;192;197;206m field model is incomplete. The six dimensions the simple model does not capture (provenance, reversibility, date-of-death conflict, downstream cascade, hidden-duplicate revelation, multi-decade lifecycle) is the recipe's strongest single passage of data-modeling pedagogy on the deceased-patient dimension. The "Death-Event Sources and Their Properties" subsection (SSA DMF with LADMF certification, state vital-records death feeds with VRDR FHIR-based modernization in progress, payer death feeds via CMS Medicare Beneficiary Database and commercial payers, EHR-and-facility-recorded deaths, hospice agency deaths, family-reported deaths, obituary feeds, claims-cessation inferences, provider-reported deaths) is correct and at the right grain, with the per-source authority / latency / completeness / accessibility characterization exactly right. The "Reconciliation Problem at Scale" nine-dimension enumeration (multi-source death-event matching, cross-source date-of-death reconciliation, premature-death-report detection and reversal, hidden-duplicate revelation handling, per-system propagation cadence, sensitivity-aware family-communication path, HIPAA-posthumous-protection-period enforcement, date-of-death-driven retrospective claims and analytics adjustment, family-reported-death intake operational discipline) is correct and recipe-specific. The "Why It Is Harder Than It Sounds" six-bullet enumeration (heterogeneous-and-changing source landscape, substantial data-quality variance across sources, broad-and-idiosyncratic downstream-cascade landscape, premature-death-report-reversal pathway as its own operational program, multi-decade HIPAA-posthumous-protection-period operational discipline, hidden-duplicate-revelation as own operational cascade) is correct and recipe-specific. The "Where the Field Has Moved" subsection (vital-records-feed modernization with FHIR-based VRDR profile, SSA DMF access landscape stable but constrained, payer death-feed integration matured for CMS MBD, hospice-and-palliative-care data integration growing, patient-portal and personal-representative frameworks evolving via CMS Patient Access API, cross-recipe coordination patterns emerging, operational metrics for deceased-patient-resolution effectiveness becoming standardized) is correctly granular and forward-looking.[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    14[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    15[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;192;197;206mThe six-stage architecture (ingest death events from the multi-source landscape with per-event provenance and source-quality classification, match each event against the institution's MPI under the deceased-patient-resolution tolerance, reconcile multi-source death events for the same patient with date-of-death-conflict-resolution and premature-death-report verification and hidden-duplicate-revelation detection, apply the death-status update to the MPI atomically with any duplicate-resolution actions, propagate the update to the downstream operational systems on each system's appropriate cadence, operate the cross-cutting concerns of HIPAA posthumous-protection-period enforcement and premature-death-report reversal and family-correspondence-after-death monitoring and audit and analytics) is the right shape for the problem. The per-source provenance and source-quality classification primitive (the death-event ingestion captures per-event provenance and a source-quality classification that the downstream pipeline consumes at every decision point) is the recipe's strongest single architectural primitive on the multi-source-reconciliation dimension. Atomic MPI update with coordinated cross-recipe actions is correctly framed as transactional discipline. Per-system cascade-propagation cadence configuration is correctly framed as discipline rather than convenience. Premature-death-report verification queue with named operational ownership is correctly elevated. HIPAA-posthumous-protection-period access-control engine is correctly elevated as multi-decade discipline. Cross-recipe coordination signals (5.1 internal duplicates, 5.5 cross-facility, 5.7 longitudinal name change, 5.8 privacy-preserving, 5.9 national-scale TEFCA, plus recipe 3.6 fraud detection, plus recipes 7.x predictive analytics and 12.x time series consuming the consolidated date-of-death) are correctly architected as first-class concerns through the EventBridge fan-out. Family-correspondence-after-death monitoring as the most family-visible operational-quality signal is correctly elevated. Operational metrics enable continuous improvement is the right framing.[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    16[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    17[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;192;197;206mThe Honest Take is the recipe's most operationally pointed section, with eleven observations earning the recipe's voice: the technical-complexity-moderate-integration-complexity-high-operational-complexity-significant-institutional-and-compassion-complexity-load-bearing framing (the recipe's strongest single observation about why deceased-patient resolution is hard), the data-integration-project-trap (the recipe's strongest single trap on the family-experience dimension), the under-investing-in-the-verification-and-reversal-pathway trap, the under-investing-in-the-family-reported-death-intake trap, the under-investing-in-cross-system-propagation trap, the matching-is-the-same-but-the-operational-discipline-is-what-distinguishes-the-program observation, the heterogeneous-source-landscape-is-going-to-remain-heterogeneous observation, the SSA-DMF-three-year-restricted-access-window-is-operationally-consequential observation, the premature-death-reports-small-in-proportion-acute-in-impact observation, the family-experience-layer-is-the-most-institution-visible-measure observation, the HIPAA-posthumous-protection-period-50-year-discipline-exceeds-institutional-planning-cycles observation, the personal-representative-framework-is-the-institution's-primary-touchpoint-with-family-during-estate-administration observation, the cross-recipe-coordination-deceased-patient-resolution-benefits-most-from-being-last observation, the would-do-differently-the-second-time observation on family-experience-and-institutional-dignity framing at program-design rather than operational-incident stage, the framework's-long-term-viability observation with the multi-decade-institutional-capability framing, and the closing dignity-the-families-deserve framing that frames deceased-patient resolution as moral-as-much-as-technical with the engineering-serving-the-framing posture. The Variations and Extensions section (authorized-intermediary LADMF subscription, state-vital-records FHIR-based feed integration, cross-network death-event propagation through TEFCA, hospice-data-network deceased-patient-source integration, pharmacy-network deceased-patient-fraud-detection integration, cohort-survival-analysis cohort-refresh automation, quality-measurement-pipeline deceased-patient-handling automation, family-bereavement-aware-communication-path opt-in framework, personal-representative-portal patient-record-access workflow, multi-decade-archival-pathway lifecycle automation, cross-jurisdictional posthumous-protection-overlay engine, active-learning-driven matching-tolerance tuning, audit-summary delivery to the personal representative) is well-scoped and frames each extension at the right grain.[K
